ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT San Marino FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between Canada and the Republic of SAN MARINO for the EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
